      <title>悉尼房价飙升可能导致城市“无孙”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/soaring-sydney-housing-may-lead-to-city-with-no-grandchildren</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新南威尔士州生产力专员警告称，悉尼高得令人瞠目结舌的房价正导致年轻家庭大量外流，如果不能扭转这一趋势，澳大利亚这座海港城市可能会被称为“没有孙子”的地方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/soaring-sydney-housing-may-lead-to-city-with-no-grandchildren</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 03:29:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
